{"tid":175841,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［古典］學左古典音樂（小提琴）好撚多年之你問我答","createTime":"2017-03-27T18:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T01:37:33.000Z","uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"493c5c578cbf22c26dfedd76557e6da823b3f2c2","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"小提琴同古典嘢都問得<br />\n講拉琴就唔係好勁（好耐之前考得個LT)<br />\n但講music concept我諗我都見得下人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 純粹覺得自己有啲嘢可以貢獻下LIHKG"},{"pid":"46daa4fd8dc6be920a3c8ee3d32d93abee2cea48","tid":175841,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"Viola撚留名"},{"pid":"d3795d480d447da1ff72aee7d3aea9445b05b15c","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:23:25.000Z","msg":"見夜媽媽人少少<br />\n我就拋下磚先<br />\n<br />\n講起古典音樂，大家有咩睇法？<br />\n悶？有錢玩意？老餅先啱？<br />\n其實古典音樂只係一個好籠統既概念<br />\n咁講，單春同陳小春都唔同啦<br />\n古典音樂上所謂既common practice period<br />\n橫跨300年 你覺得真係咁簡單？"},{"pid":"a0a692864b3f305009ad23d7213756687843857c","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:29:40.000Z","msg":"古典音樂其實係西方音樂所謂既正統<br />\n可以大概分做<br />\n1. Renaissance<br />\n2. Baroque <br />\n3. Classical<br />\n4. Romantic<br />\n(5) Late Romantic<br />\n6. 20th century<br />\n<br />\n如無意外我就該會由頭講起<br />\n大家俾我慢慢打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0c7aa8844d7d92be7b3929aab956b431dc5680","tid":175841,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:53:25.000Z","msg":"35歲先學會唔會有好大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10e8261314d3de617516cb383be79f3f519d587","tid":175841,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T19:02:41.000Z","msg":"樓主不如我地夾手夾腳搞下呢個post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/130343/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/130343/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"fc45b1753bc599dad89fbf4dd1c9bf355b45b545","tid":175841,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T20:24:00.000Z","msg":"小提琴係咪唔可以自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有玩開結他,中意小提琴既聱音,不過好似係複雜好多倍,按錯1MM都走音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果樓主話唔可以自學既話,都係打消念頭,窮毒J負擔重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29812dca1934c31264259c3d9cbf6783aac6c926","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>35歲先學會唔會有好大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n攻唔到頂<br />\n但係拉到八級應該唔難"},{"pid":"4a710f4ebef89972b6e95fbb8b327658aad39573","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小提琴係咪唔可以自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有玩開結他,中意小提琴既聱音,不過好似係複雜好多倍,按錯1MM都走音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果樓主話唔可以自學既話,都係打消念頭,窮毒J負擔重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話唔可以自學<br />\n不過極難又易錯姿勢<br />\n有人睇住先唔會走歪路<br />\n初學好平架<br />\n想學就學囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba9f90da0ee1fb6f20693409429fe6417751c8d","tid":175841,"uid":27878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"Lt都唔廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想學樓主咁開下post講下classical music<br />\n支持留名<br />\n<br />\n利申：多數聽chamber/ solo sonata，大型編制既對音響要求好撚高，去聽音樂會算"},{"pid":"ade07539e5ef6f82c9a05427c929336193710888","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"［理論多多］<br />\n學小提琴點解姿勢咁緊要？<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家知唔知日本弓道<br />\n佢地有句名言叫做「正射必中」<br />\n日本弓道講求過程<br />\n由拎起弓箭一刻<br />\n通過繁重既儀式感<br />\n達到佢地射中靶既結果<br />\n所謂正射必中係指<br />\n如果你之前的每一個步驟姿勢都啱既時候<br />\n最後一定會正中紅心<br />\n<br />\n我覺得小提琴講求既野係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姿勢啱就靚聲<br />\n要姿勢啱就要重複練習<br />\n今每一個動作成為自己既肌肉記憶"},{"pid":"bf7eba77fb5e7b25cb412d23f0dd83cb37a031e2","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lt都唔廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想學樓主咁開下post講下classical music<br />\n支持留名<br />\n<br />\n利申：多數聽chamber/ solo sonata，大型編制既對音響要求好撚高，去聽音樂會算</blockquote><br />\n我都有玩音響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買對712加部cdp 已經好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59a49b4cc18f268a3a4f63341b9eb484583f81d","tid":175841,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主不如我地夾手夾腳搞下呢個post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/130343/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/130343/page/1?ref=android</a></blockquote><br />\n諗住係度都會俾listening suggestion<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打完依個post先"},{"pid":"929f2403ec18a900f6780306bd659e2a4c00d5a3","tid":175841,"uid":27878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"我起度諗啦<br />\n其實classical咁闊<br />\n就算自己聽開 有啲類都未必岩自己口味<br />\n例如我自己本身對法國派 opera無咩好感<br />\n變相好難討論<br />\n應該按返類別 開細post 再搵個大post整合 會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但咁做人又會太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372473a065ec29cd609a62fe4244acefe04c0ff6","tid":175841,"uid":27878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我起度諗啦<br />\n其實classical咁闊<br />\n就算自己聽開 有啲類都未必岩自己口味<br />\n例如我自己本身對法國派 opera無咩好感<br />\n變相好難討論<br />\n應該按返類別 開細post 再搵個大post整合 會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但咁做人又會太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係piano concerto<br />\nPiano sonata<br />\n已經可以分兩個範疇講好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd4ec1d558a458cab12f9e52263e695be204852","tid":175841,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我起度諗啦<br />\n其實classical咁闊<br />\n就算自己聽開 有啲類都未必岩自己口味<br />\n例如我自己本身對法國派 opera無咩好感<br />\n變相好難討論<br />\n應該按返類別 開細post 再搵個大post整合 會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但咁做人又會太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係piano concerto<br />\nPiano sonata<br />\n已經可以分兩個範疇講好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 好多人話自己聽 但係冇咩好討論<br />\n只要聽既唔係同一樣野已經好難討論"},{"pid":"dca4333cc2ccc44d8e5b2339be06f29dadcd0e0e","tid":175841,"uid":128062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}